WEBVTT

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:30.720
(Laughter)

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.870
You all agree?

00:07:31.908 --> 00:07:33.488
We try to act cool?

00:07:33.522 --> 00:07:37.272
(Applause)

00:07:38.299 --> 00:07:40.079
Now, some people are cool.

00:07:40.267 --> 00:07:42.517
Like you, you know?
You don't have to try.

00:07:42.547 --> 00:07:45.390
(Cheers)

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.376
SRK: Great information for people
watching at home.

00:07:48.400 --> 00:07:51.096
For both mothers and fathers,

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:53.740
that listen from your heart
to what your children say.

00:07:53.764 --> 00:07:56.016
Even though Shelja said it was filmi,

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:59.696
I found it really beautiful:
you, me and us,

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.816
sitting together
and discussing everything.